body: Switching reviewers in an attempt to load balance
Updated to also include a thread local that caches g_min_time to avoid cacheline contention in very high throughput cases.
Fixed a slew of bugs, added a bunch of tracing that'll hopefully help in case we ever need to dive into this code again: I'm still not convinced it's entirely right.
This is looking pretty safe to merge
